 2023-05662023-06-08FIN
ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectOrder Amending the Ukraine Goods Remission Order
PrecisOrder Amending the UKRAINE GOODS REMISSION ORDER in order to remit customs duties paid or payable under the CUSTOMS TARIFF, as well as anti-dumping and countervailing duties paid or payable under the SPECIAL IMPORT MEASURES ACT, for all goods originating in Ukraine and imported into Canada, with the exception of over-access supply-managed products after June 9, 2023, unless these goods were already in transit to Canada on or before that date.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2023-0121 Publication Date: 2023-06-21
